    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Available now is a well-maintained vehicle in good condition, perfect for someone looking for a dependable and attractive ride. The engine runs smoothly and all major systems are functioning as they should, reflecting a consistent maintenance history. While the exterior looks great overall, there are a few minor stone chips and light interior wear consistent with careful regular use. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that offers a great balance of reliability and comfort for its next owner.",
