      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence. Maintained to a concours standard, the vehicle exhibits an impeccable exterior profile paired with an interior that remains in showroom condition. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a meticulously preserved specimen that offers both mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection. For the collector who accepts no compromises, this offering stands as a benchmark of its class.",
